reviewText: Great story, well told. I love the actual footage!
I enjoyed this DVD on Buffalo Bill Cody. What made it so special was that I visited his museum in Cody, Wyoming this summer and I learned a lot of information about the man.

My husband and I had a great interest in his life story.  I bought what turned out to be fake cards of his Wild West show at a local flea market.  It doesn't really matter to me since they have renewed my interest in history.  Great seller, great video; would recommend this seller highly!!!
I gave this to my brother.  We found it so enjoyable and especially since Buffalo Bill is an ancestor!  Was glad to get it at such a reasonable price.
